<p>Wow! She is known for her iconic curves and Gemma Collins showcased her dramatic three stone weight loss in a pink shimmering gown from her own Gemma Collins Collection</p>

<p>She rocked a dusty pink gown with a plunging neckline and glitzy baroque print. </p>

