<p>On Sunday, she switched up her glamorous style and cut a casual figure as she enjoyed a day out in London.   </p>

<p>Pretty in pink: The Essex diva, 39, switched up her glamorous style and  cut a casual figure in a hooded jacket and jeans as she enjoyed a day out in London on Sunday</p>

<p>She was seen sporting a lavender and pink tie-dye hoodie which complemented her pink circular shades. </p>

